Package: fhfa.gov
Title: Federal Housing Finance Agency (FHFA) House Price Index Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for FHFA House Price Index data. Master HPI,
    state/metro/regional quarterly indexes, annual tract data, and summary tables.
    All functions return tibbles with typed columns.
